    <!-- Right Column -->
    <section class="page-content-column">
      <div class="page-section">
      <h2>On the front cover</h2>
<p>The image on the front page of this website is a grayscale representation of a map I created titled <a href="" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hawaiʻi:Seafloor to Summit</a>. The image shows the full vertical extent—from seafloor to summit—of a portion of the eight main Hawaiian Islands represented using a topobathymetric DEM and hillshading.</p>
      </div>
  <div class="page-section">
      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
<p>The image on the front page of this website is a black-and-white representation of a map I created titled <a href="" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hawaiʻi:Seafloor to Summit</a>. The image shows the full vertical extent—from seafloor to summit—of a portion of the eight main Hawaiian Islands represented using a topobathymetric DEM and hillshading.</p>
      </div>
       

    
    </section>
